{"title":"拖拉机（深县庙会上的试验）","authors":["徐德表"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（深县庙会上的试验）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐德表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呜！呜！呜！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机的马达响着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它象个“水怪”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸引着庙会上的人群；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向城外流去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×    ×    ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到郊外一块平地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘟！嘟！嘟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它咆哮了几声，表演起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串的犁盘伸进土里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈来宽的土浪在它后边翻起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眨眼就是一拖长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几分钟就耕完了一亩地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万只眼睛盯着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数的人都称赞惊奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个说：“比牛劲大得多，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个说：“耕的又宽又深又整齐，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个说：“你看多么好，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个说：“不吃不喝又不费力；”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个说：“好是好，可是咱买不起，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个说：“政府贷款无问题，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个说：“这个老百姓谁会驶？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个说：“不用愁保管有人教会你。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}